Since 9th April 2019, stable branches of Rails use Buildkite for automated testing, and the list of tested ruby versions, by rails branch, is:

Rails 6.0
>= 2.5.0

Rails 5.2
>= 2.2.2

Rails 5.1
>= 2.2.2

Rails 5.0
>= 2.2.2

Rails 4.2
>= 1.9.3

Rails 4.1
>= 1.9.3

